00:19:47,640 --> 00:19:48,840
I know it.

358
00:20:01,520 --> 00:20:03,760
Morning. How'd you sleep?

359
00:20:05,240 --> 00:20:06,400
Like a baby.

360
00:20:10,360 --> 00:20:13,440
So, I thought after breakfast,
we could go to the Palick exhibit.

361
00:20:13,520 --> 00:20:15,960
He's only in town another week.

362
00:20:16,040 --> 00:20:18,520
I would love to, really,
but I am already late

