369
00:20:37,480 --> 00:20:38,480
Next time.

370
00:20:45,760 --> 00:20:47,640
Call me tonight.

371
00:20:47,720 --> 00:20:49,880
I can come over after work.

372
00:20:49,960 --> 00:20:51,040
If you want.

373
00:21:00,440 --> 00:21:03,720
