for the inmates.

381
00:22:41,880 --> 00:22:43,560
Those are in the storage room.

382
00:22:44,720 --> 00:22:47,720
But then, of course,
you already knew that.

383
00:22:49,200 --> 00:22:54,400
The one thing
I won't tolerate is dishonesty.

384
00:22:58,160 --> 00:22:59,640
You were trying to escape,
weren't you?

385
00:22:59,720 --> 00:23:00,720
No.

386
00:23:02,000 --> 00:23:03,920
I'll tell you what

387
00:23:04,000 --> 00:23:06,080
I'm gonna shoot you in the stomach.

388
00:23:06,160 --> 00:23:08,040
You'll feel pressure at first.

389
00:23:09,320 --> 00:23:12,280
Then you'll feel an intense burning
like you've never felt in your life.

390
00:23:12,360 --> 00:23:16,920
Maybe that will properly motivate you
to be honest with me.

391
00:23:17,000 --> 00:23:20,640
I ask you again.
Were you trying to escape?

392
00:23:24,480 --> 00:23:27,520
- No.
- How disappointing.

393
