00:25:46,000 --> 00:25:48,040
He said Reggie would be
at a shooting gallery.

432
00:25:49,400 --> 00:25:51,280
That's not the same as
a gun range, silly.

433
00:25:52,680 --> 00:25:54,200
You really need to get out more.

434
00:26:03,920 --> 00:26:05,520
All right, all right, all right.

435
00:26:10,040 --> 00:26:11,680
Now, go get yourself cleaned up.

436
00:26:14,000 --> 00:26:15,120
I'll be back in a minute.

437
00:26:23,920 --> 00:26:25,320
So...

438
00:26:25,400 --> 00:26:27,160
Shall we discuss terms?

439
00:26:30,960 --> 00:26:32,880
- So, what is it?
- Well, to be clear.

440
00:26:32,960 --> 00:26:34,880
This isn't an actual piece of crime
scene evidence.

441
00:26:34,960 --> 00:26:36,400
It's gone, as far as I can tell.

442
00:26:36,480 --> 00:26:38,960
What I was able to find
is a photocopy buried

443
00:26:39,040 --> 00:26:40,320
deep in a logbook.

