00:27:30,200 --> 00:27:31,560
Wonderful...

463
00:27:31,640 --> 00:27:32,640
Darling.

464
00:27:37,160 --> 00:27:38,320
And how was yours?

465
00:27:41,040 --> 00:27:42,040
Good.

466
00:27:43,560 --> 00:27:44,560
Thank you for asking.

467
00:28:05,200 --> 00:28:06,920
I think you might have been right.

468
00:28:08,080 --> 00:28:09,080
About the lamb.

469
00:28:11,080 --> 00:28:12,880
I am so sorry.

470
00:28:14,000 --> 00:28:15,000
It's fine.

471
00:28:15,080 --> 00:28:16,960
I checked it twice
when it was in the oven

472
00:28:17,040 --> 00:28:20,400
and I think it might be hotter
than it says that it is.

473
00:28:26,400 --> 00:28:27,400
You know.

474
00:28:31,880 --> 00:28:34,000
I don't think this is working out.

475
00:28:36,240 --> 00:28:37,720
It's not you.

476
00:28:42,680 --> 00:28:43,680
It's me.

477
00:29:00,400 --> 00:29:02,080
We could've had something special.

478
00:29:02,160 --> 00:29:04,560
Please. Please, don't hurt me.

479
00:29:04,640 --> 00:29:07,600
You know,
I really thought you were the one.

480
00:29:13,480 --> 00:29:14,480
Please.

481
00:29:17,080 --> 00:29:20,160
Don't worry, sooner or later.

482
00:29:20,240 --> 00:29:21,240
I'll find her.

483
00:29:28,600 --> 00:29:30,160
I still don't get it.

484
00:29:31,320 --> 00:29:33,760
Why all that trouble
for this pile of bricks?

485
00:29:33,840 --> 00:29:36,040
This was never about money, Gabe.

486
00:29:36,120 --> 00:29:39,240
Not about money? What else is there?

487
00:29:39,320 --> 00:29:42,000
All kinds of things motivate people.

488
00:29:42,080 --> 00:29:44,880
Lust, ambition, envy.

489
00:29:44,960 --> 00:29:47,800
Okay, what motivated you?

490
00:29:47,880 --> 00:29:50,200
Why do you want this place so bad?

491
00:29:50,280 --> 00:29:51,280
It's simple.

492
00:29:54,080 --> 00:29:56,200
This is where,
I'm gonna kill Don Maroni.

493
00:30:06,360 --> 00:30:08,360
It's time. Are you ready?

494
00:30:08,440 --> 00:30:09,440
Let's go.

495
00:30:23,920 --> 00:30:25,480
Now, as soon as this door opens,

496
00:30:25,560 --> 00:30:28,120
