506
00:31:26,720 --> 00:31:30,200
What wonders I'm going to make
of your parts.

507
00:31:43,120 --> 00:31:44,600
See you around, doc.

508
00:31:45,760 --> 00:31:46,800
Leave him there.

509
00:31:46,880 --> 00:31:48,560
We don't have much time. Let's go.

510
00:31:48,640 --> 00:31:49,640
Go.

511
00:31:59,600 --> 00:32:00,680
This way.

512
00:32:00,760 --> 00:32:02,720
They're headed for the boat.

513
00:32:12,640 --> 00:32:14,360
What are you doing, man?
Open up the gate.

514
00:32:14,440 --> 00:32:16,480
