517
00:32:26,720 --> 00:32:28,000
Fish.

518
00:32:28,080 --> 00:32:29,520
She set us up.

519
00:32:42,200 --> 00:32:44,120
- Kelly, other side.
- Over here, come on.

520
00:32:44,200 --> 00:32:46,040
- Hurry, hurry.
- Come on.

521
00:32:47,760 --> 00:32:49,960
