didn't you?

522
00:32:50,040 --> 00:32:51,400
I lied.

523
00:33:09,440 --> 00:33:11,000
The chopper.

524
00:33:13,880 --> 00:33:14,920
Hold on.

525
00:33:28,480 --> 00:33:29,640
Fish.

526
00:33:47,400 --> 00:33:49,800
He abducts young, single,
attractive women

